
#addEvent
    h2 Novo Evento
    fieldset(style='max-width:650px')
        div.row
            div.col-sm-12
                p(style='margin-bottom:20px') Todos os campos são obrigatórios!
        div.row
            div.col-sm-6
                input#inputEventName.form-control.form-group(type='text', placeholder='Nome do evento', ng-model='eventToAdd.name')
            div.col-sm-6
                input#inputEventLocation.form-control.form-group(type='text', placeholder='Local', ng-model='eventToAdd.location')
        div.row
            div.col-sm-6
                input.form-control.form-group(type='text', placeholder='Nome do organizador', ng-model='eventToAdd.responsible.name')
            div.col-sm-6
                input.form-control.form-group(type='text', placeholder='Email do organizador', ng-model='eventToAdd.responsible.email')
        div.row(style='display:flex;align-items:center')
            div.col-sm-4
                div.input-group
                    input.form-control(uib-datepicker-popup='dd/MM/yyyy', placeholder='Data', datepicker-options='dateOptions' is-open='startDatePopup.opened' ng-model='eventToAdd.startDate')
                    span.input-group-btn
                        button.btn.btn-default(type='button', ng-click='startDatePopup.opened=true')
                            i.glyphicon.glyphicon-calendar
            div.col-sm-2 Começa às
            div.col-sm-2(style='padding-left:0')
                uib-timepicker(ng-model='eventToAdd.startTime', show-meridian='false')
            div.col-sm-2(style='width:105px;padding-left:20px') termina às
            div.col-sm-2(style='padding-left:0;')
                uib-timepicker(ng-model='eventToAdd.finishTime', show-meridian='false')
        div.row.form-group
            div.col-sm-12
                textarea.form-control(ng-model='eventToAdd.note', placeholder='Observação')
        div.row.form-group
            div.col-sm-12
                button#btnSendEventRequest.btn.btn-primary(ng-click='sendEventRequest()') Enviar Pedido de Cadastro
        div.row
            div.col-sm-12
                p (Sujeito à confirmação)
